                        Letter from the Editor 

	HAPPY NEW YEAR! I hope everyone has started this 
year with motivation and determination. This is the time 
to make some positive changes in our lives, and Your Life-
Your Choice will be here to help you out.

	A good number of our friends overseas are celebrating 
special events this month. January is still a celebration 
month for many religions and cultures. Many have enjoyed 
their Christmas festivities this past week. Pueto Rico 
celebrates Three Kings Day, and many countries celebrate 
the Ephiphany. Venezuela has a ceremony for Paradura Del 
Nino, Malaysia celebrates Hari Raya, Israel celebrates 
Tu Bi'shevat and Iceland says goodbye to their 13th Santa 
during Threttandinn. Thaipusam and Ramadan are also celebrated 
during this time. Happy Holidays to all of you. 

    Until next time Your Life-Your Choice wishes you 
health and prosperity. 

Brigitte Synesael 
Editor of Your Life-Your Choice 
