Dear Your Life-Your Choice, 

5 years ago I had a difficult decision to make. My vision
was so poor that corrective lenses were no longer helpful.
My opthalmologist suggested that I have surgery since there 
was no hope of my eyes correcting themselves. After asking 
a lot of questions, I agreed to have major surgery on both 
my eyes. The surgery required many cuts with a Diamond tip 
scalpel. 

One eye healed with tremendous success. The other 
did not. I have since had 5 more surgeries to remove the 
scar tissue and white haze which always returned and covered 
my pupil. I have had no vision in that eye now for 5 years.
The surgeries are painful, and I finally decided no more. 

I was introduced to an herbal grape seed extract. After being 
on the product for 5 weeks I started to see! I ran into the 
bathroom and looked into the mirror because I couldn't believe 
that the continuous haze I had was leaving. My roommate couldn't
believe the difference! She said there was still a small trace, 
but no where near the blockage that had been so obvious before.
After 2 more weeks there was no hazing at all!

Stephanie
Florida

